{
  "stem": "24268.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just have one lawyer within-- with-- which in the legal department-- you know, because they're different departments.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he says, I have to call the home office in South Bend and see would they allow me or not to take off the two days-- take only one day, Rosh Hashanah, the Yom Kippur, something like that.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I say, Yom Kippur-- the New Year's Eve, Rosh Hashanah, New Year's Eve and Yom Kippur, the day of the atonement.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say, and if you believe in God, and your respect your holiday, I want you to respect mine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even if I don't have-- I don't want pay, but I won't work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he walked out to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He say, I'll let you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I say, good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went back to my file, whatever I was doing then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was-- he put me on-- his hand on mine shoulder.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says, OK, Rose.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You've got your days off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then was at-- from that time on, he used to brag so much about me, brag that I'm a good worker, and all this-- just yackety-yack.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was one Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was a college degree.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She worked at the telephone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I told her about it, she said, oh, Rose.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, there's so many antisemitism.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She said, oh, Rose.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You're so sensitive, because you came from the-- from Europe, you went so much through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Sure enough, Yom-- Yom Kippur came around, Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She did not ask for permission, because she felt so sure it's a holiday which she had-- can take off.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When she came back, they fired her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then she came and she say, you know, you're so right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, he was very-- a-- he was completely different person.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
